# 🌍 **LANGUAGE TRANSLATION APP**  

A powerful and interactive language translation app built using **Gradio, GoogleTranslator, and gTTS**.  
This app translates text into multiple languages and even provides **audio output** for supported languages.  

---

## ✨ **FEATURES**  

✔️ Translate text into **multiple languages**  
✔️ Automatically detects the input language  
✔️ **Text-to-Speech (TTS)** support for selected languages  
✔️ User-friendly **Gradio** interface  

---

## 🚀 **LIVE DEMO**  

🔗 **[Try the Language Translation App Now!](https://huggingface.co/spaces/Thilak118/LanguageTranslation)**  

---

## 🛠️ **HOW IT WORKS?**  

🔹 Enter the text you want to translate  
🔹 Select the target language from the dropdown  
🔹 Click **"Submit"** to get the translated text  
🔹 If the selected language supports speech, an **audio player** will appear to listen to the translation  

